{
  "stem": "2539.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But of course, my father didn't believe in two girls playing tennis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In those days in Poland, that was not in fashion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the tennis court was cemented over and we ride our-- we rode our bicycles around it and grew-- had a little veggie patch, Lola and I, we looked after.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was later in  Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also from Lublin-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Lutsk, [SIGHS] well, I was always top of the class.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was always the best in every subject, except for gymnastics, where I was very average, very average.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But everything else, you name it and I was tops.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think that some of the kids were jealous of me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First of all, I was Jewish and they did not admit Jews to this high school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You had to be Christian and you had to-- and you had to-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had to be bright in order-- well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe the Christians got in easily.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were only a few Jewish children in the whole school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the school would have had, oh, many hundred of-- hundreds of children, probably 600 children or so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there were only-- in my class, there were only three Jewish children, three girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In other classes, there could have been one or two.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- and I'll just give you-- illuminate-- of course, all of them knew that I'm the best, because I was always first.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I got always the best marks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if the new subject-- if a new subject was introduced, even in mathematics, I was called to the blackboard to-- to hear my opinion what I think about it before the teacher actually taught the news to the class.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So-- but why-- I'll illustrate to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
